{"tid":1329090,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[銀髮族］真係好想同頭先搭枱嘅兩個銀髮爺爺講","createTime":"2019-07-18T06:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T13:57:24.000Z","uid":164382,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f02c83940e9bd47cec970e1bd1c6d7fad23fdfc9","tid":1329090,"uid":164382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:04:24.000Z","msg":"頭先去食飯同兩個老人家搭枱<br />\n食食吓佢哋開始傾近排示威遊行<br />\n本來以為又要食緊飯都俾人鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知佢哋......<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 爺爺A<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />爺爺B<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 宜家都唔理得你係咪警察㗎喇。。。唉當然最後兩邊都唔好有傷亡啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 其實又好難怪班後生，我哋都做過後生，但我哋後生嗰陣就算要捱都知幾時捱到頭呀，宜家啲後生點捱都買唔起樓，搵萬令兩萬蚊俾租都俾咗6 7000<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 係呀，搵一萬俾咗5 6000租。。。點生活呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 唉嗰個男仔殺咗個人就搞到咁大單嘢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 話啲示威者打警察。。。但你諗吓喎 警察有全副裝備㗎喎。。。<br />\n<br />\n頂我聽到已經感動到癡線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我住嗰區係公認嘅深藍<br />\n但竟然有老人家係明白我哋<br />\n我嗰吓真係好想開口同佢哋講多謝<br />\n但毒絲怕醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝你哋呀可愛嘅爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003b4a3305cea5920a4c84e09bc1a35a99d5bd12","tid":1329090,"uid":171643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:09: